Package: pvmicrosimr
Title: Agent-based modeling for Solar PV adoption by households 
Version: 0.0.2.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Wheatley", , "joe.wheatley@ucd.ie", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5932-1683"))
Description: pvmicrosimr generates simulation runs using an agent-based-model for household solar PV + battery system adoption in Ireland. The impacts of alternative economic and policy scenarios can be explored.
